-- Bradesco, Pacific Rubiales Added to Santander’s Favorite Stocks
-- B y   C h r i s t i n e   J e n k i n s
-- 2012-06-25T13:20:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-25/bradesco-pacific-rubiales-added-to-santander-s-favorite-stocks.html
Banco Bradesco SA (BBDC4)  and  Pacific
Rubiales Energy Corp. (PRE) , which operates  Colombia ’s largest oil
field, were added to Banco Santander SA’s list of favorite Latin
American stocks.  Oil company OGX Petroleo & Gas Participacoes SA and
Telefonica Brasil SA, a unit of Madrid-based Telefonica SA, were
dropped from the list, Santander analysts Jesus Gomez and
Stefano Rizzi wrote in an e-mailed note to clients.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Christine Jenkins in Bogota at 
 cjenkins28@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Papadopoulos at 
 papadopoulos@bloomberg.net  